  "prompt": "Does all the questions get answered in Quora?",
  "response": "Not every question on Quora gets answered. While many questions receive responses from users, some may go unanswered for various reasons, such as:\n\n1. **Niche Topics**: Questions that are very specific or technical might not attract enough knowledgeable users.\n2. **Ambiguity**: If a question is unclear or poorly phrased, potential responders might avoid it.\n3. **Lack of Engagement**: Some questions may not garner enough attention or interest from the community.\n4. **Timing**: Sometimes questions go unanswered simply because they haven't been seen by the right audience yet.\n\nOverall, while Quora has a large and diverse user base that often provides answers, it cannot guarantee that every question will receive a response.",
